# Project Overview  

## Objective  
To create a robust, interactive HR Attrition Dashboard that provides actionable insights on employee attrition trends across departments, age groups, and other dimensions.  

## Key Learnings  
- Automating data processes using Power Query.  
- Building efficient data models with Power Pivot.  
- Writing DAX formulas for advanced analytics.  
- Crafting professional charts and visuals to communicate insights effectively.  

## Insights Gained  
- Attrition trends by job roles, education levels, and business travel frequency.  
- Breakdown of attrition rates by gender, age group, and performance levels.  
- Identification of key drivers affecting employee attrition.  
